{
  "lesson": "WC-PB-11",
  "audioMaster": "training/playbooks/WC-PB-11-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 146.521,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "A caller wants two things: who changed it, and what it said before.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.928,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Two pages answer that between them, and you read them in order.",
      "startS": 2.228,
      "endS": 4.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "One rule before you start.",
      "startS": 5.279,
      "endS": 8.611,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "The audit trail is read only.",
      "startS": 9.442,
      "endS": 10.914,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "It's only worth anything because nobody corrects it.",
      "startS": 11.455,
      "endS": 16.4,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Open IT and Support, then Audit.",
      "startS": 16.871,
      "endS": 18.345,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "You land on the Audit Log, and the sidebar lists three pages.",
      "startS": 18.552,
      "endS": 19.448,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "You need two of them today: the Audit Log for who did what,",
      "startS": 19.882,
      "endS": 23.389,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "and Change History for the before and after.",
      "startS": 23.602,
      "endS": 24.833,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "User Activity is login history.",
      "startS": 25.062,
      "endS": 26.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "That one belongs to a different playbook.",
      "startS": 26.896,
      "endS": 33.84,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Read the log.",
      "startS": 34.24,
      "endS": 35.241,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Seven columns tell you who touched the record, when,",
      "startS": 35.899,
      "endS": 38.986,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "from which location, and from which IP address.",
      "startS": 39.189,
      "endS": 41.952,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "The change you're chasing is an Updated row.",
      "startS": 42.591,
      "endS": 45.14,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Settings changes land here too, with the module reading Settings.",
      "startS": 45.471,
      "endS": 49.173,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Don't scroll a busy log.",
      "startS": 49.944,
      "endS": 51.453,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Filter it, or search it.",
      "startS": 51.706,
      "endS": 53.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Now the page the caller actually wants.",
      "startS": 53.76,
      "endS": 55.784,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "In the sidebar, click Change History.",
      "startS": 56.117,
      "endS": 58.291,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "One quirk from today's capture: typing its address directly returned a four oh four.",
      "startS": 58.8,
      "endS": 60.41,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "So you reach it this way, through the audit sidebar, not by URL.",
      "startS": 60.697,
      "endS": 67.663,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Narrow it to the record.",
      "startS": 68.08,
      "endS": 69.326,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Filter down to the module in question so one record's changes stand alone.",
      "startS": 69.86,
      "endS": 73.891,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "You're reading a history, not editing one.",
      "startS": 74.134,
      "endS": 76.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "And here's the answer.",
      "startS": 76.821,
      "endS": 78.162,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Each change is recorded at field level: the field, its old value, its new value,",
      "startS": 78.726,
      "endS": 80.774,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "with the user and the timestamp.",
      "startS": 81.026,
      "endS": 85.82,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "That row is, literally, what was it before.",
      "startS": 86.122,
      "endS": 89.195,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Now put the two pages together.",
      "startS": 89.6,
      "endS": 91.38,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Change History gives you the field and the exact old and new values.",
      "startS": 92.262,
      "endS": 96.381,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "The Audit Log gives you the user, the date and time, and the IP address it came from.",
      "startS": 96.947,
      "endS": 101.708,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "The price changed is not an answer.",
      "startS": 102.687,
      "endS": 104.866,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "The two values are.",
      "startS": 105.087,
      "endS": 106.42,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Write the packet.",
      "startS": 107.018,
      "endS": 108.106,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "The record, the field, both values, the user, the timestamp, the IP address, and screenshots.",
      "startS": 108.106,
      "endS": 114.642,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "You never reverse the change from here.",
      "startS": 114.642,
      "endS": 117.692,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "A correction happens in the record's own module, or gets escalated.",
      "startS": 117.692,
      "endS": 122.297,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "And if the change looks unauthorized, that's a security escalation,",
      "startS": 122.297,
      "endS": 126.172,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "and the next tier wants the IP and the user first.",
      "startS": 126.172,
      "endS": 130.16,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "That's the order.",
      "startS": 130.56,
      "endS": 131.552,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Audit Log first, for who, when, where, and which IP.",
      "startS": 132.174,
      "endS": 133.286,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Change History second, for the field-level old to new.",
      "startS": 133.575,
      "endS": 136.391,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Then the exact answer, or a clean escalation.",
      "startS": 136.809,
      "endS": 138.082,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Nothing edited, nothing touched.",
      "startS": 138.46,
      "endS": 146.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}